{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, before you went into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, nobody knew about our family, because it was a mixed family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not a religious family running to the temple or anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody-- they thought more that we are Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the Czechs never distinguished between Austrians and Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because my parents were Viennese, and we always talked German, so to the Czechs, we were Germans, never Jews, you know, till--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was so excited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remembered that in, in Goldie's flat-- in the-- in the meantime, his parents were also deported that year that I tried, you know, to work out what I am to do.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I still had the key, and the place was still empty.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remembered that we had to have black curtains for-- because of, of air-- what is it called?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, at night, the whole city had to be black.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remembered they were black felt curtains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went back into the flat, and I pulled them down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had a sleeping bag made out of the black curtains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Worst thing, because when you have fleas in a sleeping bag, it's the worst thing that can happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyhow, I had that sleeping bag made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and I prepared for-- I was so excited like if I would go to the Riviera, you know, that I'm on the 19th of May going to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were permitted, I don't know, 80, 80 kilos of, of-- that's quite a lot of stuff.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I came to the-- to Theresienstadt, the, the train was already going through the-- through the city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were brought right into, into the middle of the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
